source.name: True Value Vs Ace
source.description:
SBA Portfolio Performance by Franchise Code - Data as of 09/30/2011
Combined 7(a) & 504 loan performance data based on loans approved between 10/01/2001 and 09/30/2011, which were designated with a franchise code* and
subsequently disbursed. This list is redacted to 10 or more disbursements per franchising brand.
